title: 220. American Purpose
itunes:title: 220. American Purpose
description: The world around us is crumbling, and it's our obligation as Americans to fix these issues. In today's episode, Andy explains how society is working to keep us from realizing our true potential and how taking your personal development seriously can improve America as a whole.
